modelhub.Aggregate.unique_sessions¶

Aggregate.unique_sessions(data, groupby=NotSet.token)[source]¶

Calculate the unique sessions in the Objectiv data.

Parameters

  • data (bach.dataframe.DataFrame) – bach.DataFrame to apply the method on.

  • groupby (Union[List[Union[str, bach.series.series.Series]], str, bach.series.series.Series, sql_models.constants.NotSet]) –

    sets the column(s) to group by.

    • if not_set it defaults to using ModelHub.time_agg.

    • if None it aggregates over all data.

Returns

series with results.

Return type

bach.series.series_numeric.SeriesInt64
